@startuml
title Order Creation Sequence Flow (Based on schema.prisma)

actor "User" as User
participant "Product/SKU" as Product
participant "CartItem" as Cart
participant "AddressShip" as Address
participant "Voucher" as Voucher
participant "Order" as Order
participant "Payment" as Payment
participant "Transaction" as Transaction
participant "Shop" as Shop

== Product Discovery & Cart ==
User -> Product: View Product Details
User -> Cart: Add Item to Cart (skuId, quantity)
activate Cart
Cart -> Product: Validate Stock
Cart --> User: Item Added
deactivate Cart

== Checkout Process ==
User -> Address: Select/Create Shipping Address
User -> Voucher: Apply Voucher (optional)
activate Voucher
Voucher --> User: Voucher Valid/Invalid
deactivate Voucher

User -> Order: Place Order
activate Order
Order -> Product: Reserve Stock (SKU)
Order -> Voucher: Lock Voucher Usage
Order -> Order: Calculate Total (Price + Shipping - Discount)
Order -> Shop: Notify New Order
Order --> User: Order Created (PENDING)
deactivate Order

== Payment Process ==
User -> Payment: Initiate Payment
activate Payment
Payment -> Transaction: Create Transaction Record
activate Transaction
Transaction --> Payment: Transaction Created
deactivate Transaction
Payment -> Payment: Process Payment (External Gateway)
Payment -> Order: Update Order Status (PAID)
Payment --> User: Payment Success
deactivate Payment

@enduml
